@startuml
component "GUI (Dashboard)" as UI
component "Backend API" as API
database "Local DB (SQLite)" as DB
component "WebSocket" as RT
component "Vision Pipeline" as CV
component "Alert Manager" as AM
UI --> API : REST/JSON
UI --> RT : WebSocket events
API --> CV : process frames / extract features
API --> DB : read/write sessions & events
API --> AM : evaluate thresholds + cooldown
AM --> RT : alert_triggered
@enduml
